  "body": "Light clients that use `compact_committees_roots` as their authentication root for the active validator pool do not benefit from the mixing of `active_index_roots` in `get_seed`. Indeed, an attacker can fiddle with `compact_committees_roots` while keeping `active_index_roots`   fixed (and hence keeping the shuffling fixed).",
